{"sectionId":745,"sectionIdLiteral":"745","humanId":"lesson-323","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I gladly make the ‚Äúsacrifice‚Äù of fear.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 323"},"annotation":"W-323","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-323\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"745#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"745#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Here is the only ‚Äúsacrifice‚Äù You ask of Your beloved Son; You ask him to give up all suffering, all sense of loss and sadness, all anxiety and doubt, and freely let Your Love come streaming in to his awareness, healing him of pain, and giving him Your Own eternal joy.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"745#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Such is the ‚Äúsacrifice‚Äù You ask of me, and one I gladly make; the only ‚Äúcost‚Äù of restoration of Your memory to me, for the salvation of the world.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"745#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"745#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>And as we pay the debt we owe to truth,‚Äîa debt that merely is the letting go of self-deceptions and of images we worshipped falsely‚Äîtruth returns to us in wholeness and in joy.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"745#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>We are deceived no longer.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"745#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Love has now returned to our awareness.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"745#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>And we are at peace again, for fear has gone and only love remains.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Here is the only ‚Äúsacrifice‚Äù You ask of Your beloved Son; You ask him to give up all suffering, all sense of loss and sadness, all anxiety and doubt, and freely let Your Love come streaming in to his","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 323: I gladly make the ‚Äúsacrifice‚Äù of‚Ä¶ | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in M